{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|ls=ic|天|雨|t1=person|t2=rain}} — a person getting wet in the rain. Original character of {{och-l|濡|to get wet}}. The component {{zh-l|*天}} corrupted into {{zh-l|*而}} during the Han dynasty.

